Definition: evergreen mat-forming shrub of North America and northern Eurasia having small white flowers and red berries
Example: leaves turn red in autumn
Synonyms: red_bearberry, wild_cranberry, mealberry, hog_cranberry, sand_berry, sandberry, mountain_box, bear, s_grape, creashak, Arctostaphylos_uva-ursi, bearberry, evergreen, mat-forming, shrub, of, North, America, and, northern, Eurasia, having, small, white, flowers, red, berries, leaves, turn, in, autumn
Category: noun.plant
